//BACKEND
1. Clone Backend folder, run "npm init -y" to install all deps
2. initiate "node server.js"
3. backend starts to run LOCALLY (PORT:5000)
4. already backend is deployed on RENDER for easy demo

//FRONTEND
1. Clone Frontend folder, run "npm install" to install all deps
2. initiate "npm run dev"
3. frontend runs LOCALLY (PORT:3000)

//TO RUN THIS PROJECT LOCALLY, YOU NEED TO CHANGE THE BASE URL TO LOCALHOST:5000 
